    <img width="320" height="550" src="https://www.quantamagazine.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FundamentalsNewsletter-Ads-Article.gif" class="fill-h" alt="Introducing Fundamentals, a new newsletter from Quanta Magazine." decoding="async" /></a>
